@startuml Admin_CompanyVerification

title Admin - Company Verification (Module B)

actor Admin as "🔐 Admin"

rectangle "COMPANY VERIFICATION" {
    usecase "List Pending\nCompanies" as CV1
    usecase "View Company\nDetails" as CV2
    usecase "Verify Tax ID" as CV3
    usecase "Approve Company" as CV4
    usecase "Reject Company" as CV5
    usecase "Ban Company\nAccess" as CV6
    usecase "Unlock Company\nAccess" as CV7
}

Admin --> CV1: 1. List companies
CV1 --> CV2: View details
CV2 --> CV3: 2. Verify tax ID
CV3 --> CV4: 3. Approve
CV3 --> CV5: 4. Reject
CV2 --> CV6: 5. Ban company
CV2 --> CV7: 6. Unlock company

note right of CV1
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
